cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a learning task from images to reason about logic relations without presetting any reasoning patterns. This involves the use of neural network models and the design of a novel network framework. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper also mentions the use of typical neural network models, which suggests the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as possible options.
